==Tailoring==
Crystal Fruit is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring|Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt064.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a blue dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*The Crystal Fruit may be randomly requested in [[Winter]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|450}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.
*One Crystal Fruit may be requested by [[Ice Pip]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].  Can be requested in a Fish Pond quest.}}

